ls0 ws0">She presents flowers to those who are celebrating birthdays, their </div><div class="t m6ec xd h12 y54e ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">baptism, or other significant milestones. Today Maria invited </div><div class="t m6d7 x38 h12 y5c6 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people who would like to follow Jesus to come forward. The </div><div class="t m52f x38 h12 y261 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">woman Maria had invited to the meeting joined the group at the </div><div class="t m1c4 x38 h12 yc4e ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">front. &quot;I have never had such a wonderful day in my life,&quot; she </div><div class="t m6b3 x38 h12 y5af ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">testified. Maria wondered if the woman felt pressured to come </div><div class="t m6ed x38 h12 y264 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forward, but the woman said, &quot;No, you did not pressure me to </div><div class="t m102 x38 h12 yc4f ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">come. You invited me. I came because I wanted to.&quot; </div><div class="t m49 x0 h12 y5b1 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Maria looks for people with needs that she can supply. During </div><div class="t m25a x38 h12 yb94 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recent evangelistic meetings, Maria felt a burden for handicapped </div><div class="t m6ee x38 h12 yc50 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people. She wanted to invite them to the meetings but did not </div><div class="t m578 x38 h12 yafc ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">know where to find them. When she met a woman in a wheelchair, </div><div class="t m388 x38 h12 y268 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Maria asked her for names of other people confined to wheel-</div><div class="t m6a x38 h12 y269 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">chairs. She made friends with them and invited them to the meet-</div><div class="t m11a x38 h12 y26a ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ings. Many wanted to go, but they had no way to get there. </div><div class="t m6ef x0 h12 y26b ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Maria rented a bus and brought the people to the meetings. </div><div class="t m6f0 x27 h12 y26c ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">About 30 handicapped people came, and </div><div class="t m3eb x27 h12 y26d ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eight wheelchair-bound people were bap-</div><div class="t m6d3 x27 h12 y26e ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tized. The relatives were amazed that some-</div><div class="t m458 x27 h12 y5b9 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">one would do this for their loved one; no </div><div class="t m480 x27 h12 y5ba ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">one had ever cared for their spiritual needs </div><div class="t m81 x27 h12 yc51 ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">before. </div><div class="t m5b8 x6a h11 yaff ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Maria Drach is an active laywoman in </div><div class="t m2a1 x27 h11 yb00 ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sochi, Russia. Charlotte Ishkanian is editor </div><div class="t m5a7 x27 h11 yc52 ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the </div><div class="t m2cc xc2 h11 yc52 ff6 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mission </div><div class="t m354 xcb h11 yc52 ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">quarterlies. </div><div class="t m350 x6b h27 y5be ff3 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I or Currciit </div><div class="t m6f1 xba h5 y7c9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NC \\ </div><div class="t m427 x52 h27 y5be ff3 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shrCal</div><div class="t m6f2 x7f h27 y5be ff3 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.</div><div class="t m404 x4e h1b y5be ff4 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">. </div><div class="t m11d x53 h27 yc53 ff3 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cull I -800-6-I-6-5S24 </div><div class="t m11d xcc h2a yc54 ff8 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m11d xcc h2a yc55 ff8 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m394 xb7 h12 y53d ff4 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">95 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
